OL,3,CRecycling plant fined after exposing
OL,4,Cworkers to cancer-causing dust
OL,6,FA recycling plant in Middlesbrough has
OL,7,Fbeen fined after exposing workers to
OL,8,Fcancer-causing dust.
OL,10,FThe long-term health of workers at a
OL,11,Fwood waste recycling centre was said
OL,12,Fto have been put in danger due to
OL,13,Fexcessive exposure to the dust their
OL,14,Fwork created, a Health and Safety
OL,15,FExecutive (HSE) prosecution has found.
