OL,3,CRecycling plant fined after exposing
OL,4,Cworkers to cancer-causing dust
OL,6,FEsken Renewables Limited, a waste and
OL,7,Frecycling company that specialises in
OL,8,Fgenerating biofuel from renewable
OL,9,Fwaste, ran a wood waste recycling
OL,10,Fcentre that processed mixed wood
OL,11,Fwaste, hardwood and softwood into
OL,12,Fbiofuel.
OL,14,FBreathing in wood dust excessively can
OL,15,Fcause asthma and nasal cancer.
OL,17,FIn particular, dust from softwood wood
OL,18,Fis a known asthmagen while particles
OL,19,Ffrom hardwood are a known carcinogen.
