OL,3,CRecycling plant fined after exposing
OL,4,Cworkers to cancer-causing dust
OL,6,FA HSE inspector visited in April 2022
OL,7,Fto investigate the dust exposures on
OL,8,Fthe site. A few weeks earlier,
OL,9,Fconcerns had been raised about wood
OL,10,Fdust spreading to the surrounding area.
OL,12,FThe inspector wrote in detail to Esken
OL,13,FRenewables with evidence demonstrating
OL,14,Fthe extent of the wood dust exposure
OL,15,Fto staff, so that the right action
OL,16,Fcould be taken by the company to
OL,17,Fcontrol the risks.
